*Create a Shirt Model
* name, url, image_url
* Create a ShirtsController
**   index Action that shows all of the shirts
** Create a shirts/index.html.erb template
*
*/sessions/new => Login form
*SessionsController#new
*  views/sessions/new.html.erb
*POST to /sessions
*
*/registrations/new => Signup form
*POST to /registrations

* Navigation links /lessons /shirts

* Lessons are attributed to the logged in user

Lessons can be commented on by other users
  post /lessons/7/comments
